entry.title: Supreme Court considers whether Trump can be removed from a primary ballot
entry.summary: The justices will consider whether Republican front-runner Donald Trump can be disqualified from a state primary ballot because he allegedly engaged in an insurrection to try to cling to power, after he lost the 2020 election to Joe Biden.

entry.title: Airline starts weighing passengers at the gate
entry.summary: But now, some brave airline passengers are consenting to being weighed themselves before boarding the plane.

entry.title: 22-year-old woman missing for days after going hiking during historic Southern California storm
entry.summary: Lisei Huang left for a hike in the Mount Baldy area of the San Gabriel Mountains at about 2 p.m. Sunday, and she was last heard from about two hours later, the San Bernardino County Sheriff's Department said. She was reported missing Sunday night.

entry.summary: Across Russia, creaking infrastructure and a wave of accidents have plunged households into the cold in the depth of winter, fueling rare showings of public frustration.

entry.title: Marine Corps confirms the worst: All 5 troops killed in helicopter crash in California mountains
entry.summary: Five U.S. Marines aboard a helicopter that went down during stormy weather in the mountains outside of San Diego are confirmed dead, the military said Thursday.
